source.name: Beach Water Quality
source.description: Working with the San Francisco Department of Public Health (SFDPH), we jointly administer the beach water quality monitoring program in San Francisco. Both agencies participate in sample collection; the San Francisco Water, Power and Sewer Microbiology Laboratory performs bacteriological analyses.
